snippet.title: The Texas Chain Saw Massacre - IGN Exclusive Trailer
snippet.description:
A game based on true events, The Texas Chain Saw Massacre. Who will survive and what will be left of them? Coming August 18th, 2023 on Xbox Series X|S and Xbox One and will launch into Game Pass on Xbox and PC.

For more information, check out The Texas Chain Saw Massacre at TXChainSawGame.com and find us on the following social platforms:

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/TXChainSawGame/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TXChainSawGame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/TXChainSawGame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TXChainSawGame

ESRB Rating Pending.
